      <ThreadGroup guiclass="ThreadGroupGui" testclass="ThreadGroup" testname="Public REST Controller for processing Natural Language Query (NLQ) requests.
Allows merchants to query dashboard stats using plain English phrases.

Flow:
1. Receives natural language &quot;query&quot; (e.g. &quot;how are my sales today?&quot;).
2. Delegates to {@link NaturalLanguageStatParser} to translate the text into structured dates.
3. Uses {@link StatsQueryService} to fetch actual business metrics for those dates.
4. Returns both the interpreted range and the resulting statistics data." enabled="true">
        <stringProp name="ThreadGroup.on_sample_error">continue</stringProp>
        <elementProp name="ThreadGroup.main_controller" elementType="LoopController" guiclass="LoopControlPanel" testclass="LoopController" testname="LoopController" enabled="true">
